{"type":"message","id":"218bf899","parentId":"63d554a4","timestamp":"2026-04-02T02:29:35.647Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"当前只有一个 cron session，没有活跃的用户对话。最后一条消息是 cron 任务本身发出的，不是用户消息。我需要再检查一下是否有agent:main的活跃对话。\n\n从结果看，只有一个cron session，没有agent:main的活跃会话。这说明没有活跃对话，应该执行自主学习。\n\n让我先读取skill文件，然后执行自主学习。\n\n等等，这个session本身就是当前会话，所以没有\"其他\"活跃对话。但这里的规则是检查是否有\"用户消息\"。让我看看更新时间 - 这个cron session的最后更新是1775096960692（毫秒），转换成北京时间大约是现在的时间。\n\n但问题是：这个cron任务是由定时器触发的，而不是用户消息。它不是活跃对话（用户发起的对话）。\n\n规则说的是\"最近5分钟内的用户消息\"。当前只有一个cron session，没有用户对话。应该执行自主学习。\n\n让我执行自主学习 - 搜索企业数字化转型、智能安防、网络系统集成、IT运维服务等道简网络相关行业的最新动态。","thinkingSignature":"f049ae99d92e05de2e8a028ff89acf2f07e9cd3c8dfc936f18df29745f6dc867"},{"type":"text","text":"\n当前只有一个 cron session，没有用户发起的活跃对话。执行自主学习。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_d5w3z1hhqecq_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/skills/miaoda-web-search/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":823,"output":246,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45050,"cost":{"input":0.0002469,"output":0.00029519999999999997,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00186153}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775096966893}}
{"type":"message","id":"a55ff576","parentId":"218bf899","timestamp":"2026-04-02T02:29:35.654Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_d5w3z1hhqecq_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\r\nname: miaoda-web-search\r\ndescription: \"ALWAYS use this skill FIRST when you need to find, look up, or verify ANY information from the internet — do NOT guess URLs and fetch them directly. Provides necessary command usage instructions for keyword-based web search with AI-generated summaries. 触发词：搜索, 网页搜索, 搜一下, 查一下, 查询, 了解, 找一下, 帮我看看, web search, look up, find out, search, 搜索摘要, 查资料, 搜索引擎, 最新信息, 最近动态\"\r\noverride-tools:\r\n  - web_search\r\n---\r\n\r\n# Web Search\r\n\r\n通过 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary` 按关键词搜索互联网信息，由 AI 自动总结。\r\n\r\n## Quick Reference\r\n\r\n| 参数 | 说明 | 必需 | 默认值 |\r\n|------|------|------|--------|\r\n| `--query` | 搜索关键词（1-500 字符） | 是 | - |\r\n| `--output, -o` | 输出格式: text/json | 否 | text |\r\n\r\n## 命令选择决策树\r\n\r\n```\r\n用户想获取互联网信息\r\n├─ 有具体 URL → miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n├─ 无具体 URL，需搜索 → miaoda-studio-cli search-summary\r\n└─ 先搜索再深入 → search-summary 获取 URL → web-crawl 提取详情（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 使用示例\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n# 按关键词搜索\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"React 19 新特性\"\r\n\r\n# 搜索并获取 JSON 输出\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"ByteDance 开源项目\" --output json\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Common Mistakes\r\n\r\n| 错误 | 正确做法 |\r\n|------|----------|\r\n| 无具体 URL 时用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl` | 无 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary`，有 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl`（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill） |\r\n| 搜索关键词超过 500 字符 | 提炼核心关键词，保持精简 |\r\n| 需要后续程序处理结果但未加 `--output json` | 需要解析结果时始终加 `--output json` |\r\n| 命令失败后不检查退出码 | 退出码 `1` 表示失败，检查参数和网络后重试 |\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775096975650}}
{"type":"message","id":"a1bd2d2e","parentId":"a55ff576","timestamp":"2026-04-02T02:29:41.315Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，我需要使用 miaoda-studio-cli search-summary 来搜索企业数字化转型、智能安防、网络系统集成、IT运维服务等道简网络相关行业的最新动态。让我搜索几个关键词。","thinkingSignature":"5ebba4b1f5fcf7e4e9c304928d2ac84cbb2292fb1d2a6f9aaba6811e42a43534"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_dsc8fdzr79jh_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"企业数字化转型最新动态 2026\" --output json 2>/dev/null | head -200","timeout":30}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_dsc8fdzr79jh_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"智能安防行业发展趋势 2026\" --output json 2>/dev/null | head -200","timeout":30}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_dsc8fdzr79jh_3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"IT运维服务行业发展动态 2026\" --output json 2>/dev/null | head -200","timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1584,"output":221,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45786,"cost":{"input":0.0004752,"output":0.0002652,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00205983}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775096975653}}
